{"tid":419869,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴敏華：倘23條立法要離婚","createTime":"2017-10-01T00:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T03:05:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"112ab9021644eda8f073089e6e0678bb6b5b5710","tid":419869,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:43:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20169403&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20169403%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171001&d=09vax6lzV43gmAJtBMTy7uargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=2651bf04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20169403%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171001&h=7e6fe8a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20169403&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171001</a><br />\n<br />\n嚴敏華：倘23條立法要離婚<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n   <img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171001/large/01la4p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171001%2Flarge%2F01la4p3.jpg&h=dd232deb&s={SIZE}\" />     <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反新界東北發展案13子之一、社民連成員嚴敏華（圖）在獄中家書中談到政治打壓對家庭的影響。她對自己成為政治犯，將社運圈外的丈夫拉入政治泥沼而感到內疚，更擔心將來若23條立法，為免政治迫害拖累丈夫，可能要和他離婚。<br />\n<br />\n憂拖累丈夫受政治迫害<br />\n<br />\n嚴敏華兩年前與來自非洲的丈夫結婚，她在給母親的信中透露，上周日探訪時與丈夫短暫獨處，只可以隔着玻璃講話。她感到內疚，因丈夫是單純老實人，一心只想努力工作求得與家人一起安居樂業。「即使是生活無憂的人，要遵守結婚誓詞都難了，何況我還是一個冥頑不靈的政治犯？或者只有像他這樣堅韌的男人，才可以承受如此拖累他的老婆」。<br />\n<br />\n嚴又表示，中共打擊異見的拿手好戲，便是傾盡制度之利去摧漽個人及其家庭，很後悔把他也拉入這個無盡苦楚的泥沼。<br />\n她擔心一旦23條立法，她可能會遇到劉曉波與李旺陽的相同遭遇。為免丈夫被拖累，她可能要與他離婚。「他雖明白我為何受苦，但這種苦楚也加諸於他身上時，我心是何等的痛－不能接受所愛的人受傷！」<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t赴英論壇　林淳軒：港已變獨裁<br />\n要聞 3小時前<br />\n\t眾志「自囚」撐良心犯　今上街反威權支聯會抗議中共欺壓維權者<br />\n要聞 3小時前[/img]"},{"pid":"86c5b9c4432843b1331a0cc404e7a2cc0e7b10de","tid":419869,"uid":146720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:51:52.000Z","msg":"無得食黑腸？"},{"pid":"a0eaebdb2499c1e50a799172c82eaa5a56155563","tid":419869,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:56:46.000Z","msg":"自比劉霞劉曉波 FF too much<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb72a7bcb5434f75ae5a5196c97e8fedf997eca","tid":419869,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"大愛黎講佢真係唔話得<br />\n嫁個黑人老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda6d56803fc349dce82015cf3cc8329f8cab612","tid":419869,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:02:38.000Z","msg":"點解女人要賤到閪咁"},{"pid":"547b350fef51e89a0b542a18824bb81ddb7aad4b","tid":419869,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:05:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大愛黎講佢真係唔話得<br />\n嫁個黑人老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想嫁港男可能比較忟水..."}]}